---
title: Caribbean Chicken Curry with Spinach Cauliflower Rice & Cashews
description: A hearty chicken spiced and wrapped up in veggies and a coconutty sauce makes for a great curry. Let’s add a little something extra
tonight and try out this chicken with spinach rice. We’re pretty sure this is a winner but we’ll leave the judging up to you.

